            Senior Web Development Manager
          </p>
          <div class="flex justify-center gap-6 text-sm text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400">
            <span>Austin, TX</span>
            <span>|</span>
            <a href="mailto:ryanclayton78@gmail.com" class="hover:text-primary-800 dark:hover:text-primary-200">ryanclayton78@gmail.com</a>
            <span>|</span>
            <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/ryan-clayton-atx" class="hover:text-primary-800 dark:hover:text-primary-200">LinkedIn</a>
            <span>|</span>
            <a href="https://github.com/feverdreaminteractive" class="hover:text-primary-800 dark:hover:text-primary-200">GitHub</a>
