                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2 mt-0.5 text-green-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  Integrated Claude AI for conversational business intelligence and automation
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2 mt-0.5 text-green-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  Managed technical teams and implemented agile development processes
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2 mt-0.5 text-green-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
